           if        p-rsc                not  = spaces
                     go to emi-seq-ini-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Set horizontal pitch                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   ecs-hor-ptc-000      thru ecs-hor-ptc-999        .
           if        p-rsc                not  = spaces
                     go to emi-seq-ini-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Set vertical pitch                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   ecs-ver-ptc-000      thru ecs-ver-ptc-999        .
           if        p-rsc                not  = spaces
                     go to emi-seq-ini-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Form Lenght, Top, Bottom                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   ecs-frm-ltb-000      thru ecs-frm-ltb-999        .
           if        p-rsc                not  = spaces
                     go to emi-seq-ini-999.
       emi-seq-ini-999.
           exit.

