                     "@"        delimited by   size
                                          into w-buf                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Concatenazione in record [stp]                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   cat-buf-rec-000      thru cat-buf-rec-999        .
